{"id": "1457848108628054067", "channel_id": "1457848108628054067", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "The Tentacle gathering passive says that she get 1 Tentacle every turn, the 2th intention say that she get 2 Temporary tentacles, and the 3th intention say that she will get 1 Temporary tentacle when she switch to that intention.\nDuring the 3th turn she should have 3 permanent ones and 3 Temporary ones, then why does she has 10 total? \nIs the fight that is bugged or is the description that is not updated between the Elite version and the Boss version?\nThis is the Boss version.", "timestamp": "2026-01-05T21:27:54.605000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-05T21:29:20.921000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1457848109093748787", "filename": "3_and_undercurrent.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 157592, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1457848108628054067/1457848109093748787/3_and_undercurrent.JPG?ex=69fefe1a&is=69fdac9a&hm=a3be14ac6f809d2b8c0c9ba792eddd2ce4a737364ef79233c91f369df525fa54&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1457848108628054067", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「Resolved」Faros Boss Strange Stuff", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960", "1361168893200044183"]}
