{"id": "1457831020526043207", "channel_id": "1457831020526043207", "type": 0, "author_id": "1437487264023318668", "author_name": "vxvendetta97", "author_bot": false, "content": "Outside of the strange and wrong translations i posted in https://discord.com/channels/1131791637933199470/1350058928020656178/1457822116396400844.\nMouchette boss have some strange interaction during the Phase transition.\nIf you fill the 10 stacks of Frenzy during it, she automatically activate the phase change and will attack while being immune and with the 80 fortress, maybe she should clear the stacks when she change phase?\n\nAnd in the phase change Intention she get 80 temporary Fortress, but she will lose it immediately when the next turn start.\nIs that a way to block bleed and other dots for damaging her between the Phases? just to make sure", "timestamp": "2026-01-05T20:20:00.484000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2026-01-05T20:27:56.140000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1457831021335679191", "filename": "p_change.JPG", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 172551, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1457831020526043207/1457831021335679191/p_change.JPG?ex=69feee30&is=69fd9cb0&hm=b7ec4ed395e4b640f5d4d548950cf36a67da9bd93cba5d44ab564703a7a280b8&"}, {"id": "1457831022472462440", "filename": "2026-01-05_21-07-19.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 12892712, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1457831020526043207/1457831022472462440/2026-01-05_21-07-19.mp4?ex=69feee30&is=69fd9cb0&hm=767e37d77b238d3d9a3b4a0be724b7000be3f254bcb247d0604c790db396bf87&"}, {"id": "1457831023625633833", "filename": "2026-01-05_21-10-25.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 9664995, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1457831020526043207/1457831023625633833/2026-01-05_21-10-25.mp4?ex=69feee31&is=69fd9cb1&hm=dc9fe6e4837aff0d4b6291944d71a5f73cb017c66031da760ceb47fcdf1314b0&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread